    "description": "The battle for the right of human habitation against the &quot;Gs&quot; that have suddenly appeared on the earth is about to begin.<br><br>You are about the same size as a cockroach, and you must use every means at your disposal to destroy the massive number of &quot;Gs&quot; that crawl on the ground, on the walls, and even fall from the ceiling.<br>Sometimes you assassinate them with guns, sometimes you blast them with bazookas. Sometimes you use lasers to reap them, sometimes you use missiles to bomb them. Don't forget the pesticides.<br><br>Complete all missions by manipulating a wide variety of weapons.<br><br>The fate of Japanese houses is in your hands.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >First, you have to mess around with weapons!</h2>The weapons you get from Gachagacha are random and their status is also random!<br>However, the more expensive gachagachas are more likely to produce stronger weapons, and weapons with stronger stats!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378720/extras/dde55e0e002b09c9e8d5f67bb9af94df.poster.avif?t=1682070466\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378720/extras/dde55e0e002b09c9e8d5f67bb9af94df.webm?t=1682070466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378720/extras/dde55e0e002b09c9e8d5f67bb9af94df.mp4?t=1682070466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Equip your weapons!</h2>Choose and equip four weapons from a wide variety of weapons!<br>Choose the weapon that best suits your combination and mission!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2378720/extras/5547068c5ea4604c4181940b4234ff73.poster.avif?t=1682070466\" width=4